						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ACan Green Hydrogen Production Help Bring Oceanic Dead Zones Back to Life?%0D%0AGreen hydrogen production makes a lot of extra oxygen. Could we put it to work revitalizing the ocean?%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/can-green-hydrogen-production-help-bring-oceanic-dead-zones-back-to-life/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



